Object.Field: RKM JDE Enterprise One DB2 AS400

COMPONENT NAME: RKM JDE Enterprise One DB2 AS400
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION: - Reverse engineering Knowledge Module to retrieve the tables for JDE Enterprise One. - This RKM is suitable for JDE installed on IBM DB2 AS400.
DB2 AS400 schema that stores the JDE Central objects.
DB2 AS400 schema that stores the JDE data dictionary.
DB2 AS400 schema that stores JDE Object Librarian.
DB2 AS400 schema that stores JDE Contral tables.
If this option is selected, data tables are reversed.
If this option is selected, interface tables (ztables) are reversed.

DE System Short Name as (set % for all JDE System) : 00 Foundation Environment 01 Adress Book 02 Electronic Mail 03 Accounts Receivable etc ...
Or you can specify a list of modeles like '01','02','03'
Language used to recover the object description and comments. List of language : E English F French S Spanish
